day, so I'm not gonna say my

afraid to take it.

239:

at least.
248:
*sniff* I'm gonna miss you guys. 
Stellie, Al, Lighteous... Even you, Nim-
Nim.

wait!
268:
Byeeee! And thanks again for saving 
me!
